The paper deals with the computational complexity of a specific subclass of label tree-based algorithms used for multi-class and multi-label problems. This makes it likely to fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), computational complexity (cs.CC), and social and information networks (cs.SI) which deal with similar topics.
